00:35:19.051 --> 00:35:20.484
Aroma de cereja.

00:35:23.989 --> 00:35:25.188
Merda.

00:35:27.426 --> 00:35:28.458
De jeito nenhum.

00:35:29.461 --> 00:35:30.827
O quê?

